tive Name Server c\\u00f3 ch\\u1ee9a c\\u00e1c th\\u00f4ng tin cho bi\\u1ebft t\\u00ean mi\\u1ec1n \\u0111ang t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm g\\u1eafn v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 IP t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng \\u1ee9ng n\\u00e0o. N\\u00f3 s\\u1ebd cung c\\u1ea5p cho Recursive Resolver \\u0111\\u1ecba ch\\u1ec9 IP trong danh m\\u1ee5c c\\u1ee7a n\\u00f3 c\\u00f3.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2 style=\\\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 21px; margin-bottom: 5px;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:36px;\\\"><strong><a id=\\\"3. C\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng DNS hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3\\u00a0\\\" name=\\\"3. C\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng DNS hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3\\u00a0\\\"><span style=\\\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight:700\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\">3. C\\u00e1ch s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng DNS hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/a><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"line-height: 1.38;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:16px;\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-variant: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight:400\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\">T\\u1ea5t c\\u1ea3 c\\u00e1c DNS Server \\u0111\\u1ec1u c\\u00f3 m\\u1ed1i li\\u00ean h\\u1ec7 m\\u1eadt thi\\u1ebft v\\u1edbi nhau. V\\u1edbi kh\\u1ed1i l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u00f4ng tin v\\u1eeba \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c tri\\u1ec3n khai \\u1edf tr\\u00ean, c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n s\\u1ebd th\\u1ea5y qu\\u00e1 nhi\\u1ec1u v\\u00e0 kh\\u00f4ng bi\\u1ebft b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng DNS t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u00e2u v\\u00e0 nh\\u01b0 th\\u1ebf n\\u00e0o \\u0111\\u1ec3 hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/