(40, 'product', 'xe-co', NULL, 'Xe cộ', '{\"image\":\"\\/data\\/cms-image\\/6.jpg\",\"image_background\":null,\"brief\":{\"vi\":null},\"content\":{\"vi\":\"<h2 style=\\\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 13px; margin-bottom: 13px; text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:15pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight:700\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\">M\\u1eaaU GIAO DI\\u1ec6N WEBSITE XE C\\u1ed8 SANG TR\\u1eccNG, \\u0110\\u1eb2NG C\\u1ea4P V\\u01af\\u1ee2T B\\u1eacC<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"line-height:1.38; text-align:justify; margin-top:13px; margin-bottom:13px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight:400\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\">Ng\\u00e0y nay, m\\u1ee9c s\\u1ed1ng con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c n\\u00e2ng cao theo s\\u1ef1 ph\\u00e1t tri\\u1ec3n c\\u1ee7a to\\u00e0n x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i. \\u0110a s\\u1ed1 ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam \\u0111\\u00e3 t\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o chi tr\\u1ea3 nh\\u1eefng nhu c\\u1ea7u t\\u1ed1i thi\\u1ec3u trong cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng nh\\u01b0 v\\u1ec1 l\\u01b0\\u01a1ng th\\u1ef1c, y t\\u1ebf,... C\\u00e2u chuy\\u1ec7n cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng kh\\u00f4ng c\\u00f2n l\\u00e0 \\u0103n \\u0111\\u1ee7 no, m\\u1eb7c \\u0111\\u1ee7 \\u1ea5m m\\u00e0 hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ea1i, nhi\\u1ec1u ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u00e3 h\\u01b0\\u1edbng t\\u1edbi vi\\u1ec7c \\u0103n sao cho ngon, m\\u1eb7c sao cho \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u00e0 di chuy\\u1ec3n sao cho thu\\u1eadn ti\\u1ec7n, an to\\u00e0n, ri\\u00eang t\\u01b0. C\\u0169ng ch\\u00ednh v\\u00ec l\\u00fd do n\\u00e0y, nhu c\\u1ea7u ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ti\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l\\u00e0 xe m\\u00e1y, \\u00f4 t\\u00f4, ng\\u00e0y c\\u00e0ng t\\u0103ng cao trong x\\u00e3 h\\u1ed9i. \\u0110\\u00e2y l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t c\\u01a1 h\\u1ed9i cho c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n, t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c kinh doanh xe c\\u1ed9, nh\\u01b0ng c\\u0169ng l\\u00e0 m\\u1ed9t th\\u00e1ch th\\u1ee9c l\\u1edbn d\\u00e0nh cho nh\\u1eefng nh\\u00e0 cung \\u1ee9ng kh\\u00f4ng t\\u1ea1o \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c n\\u00e9t \\u0111\\u1ed9t ph\\u00e1, ri\\u00eang bi\\u1ec7t trong th\\u1ecb tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng c\\u1ea1nh tranh kh\\u1ed1c li\\u1ec7t.&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"line-height:1.38; text-align:justify; margin-top:13px; margin-bottom:13px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:11pt; font-variant:normal; white-space:pre-wrap\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#000000\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight:400\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration:none\\\">M\\u1eabu giao di\\u1ec7n thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf website xe c\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u doanh nghi\\u1ec7p \\u01b0a chu\\u1ed9ng. Kh\\u00f4ng \\u00edt showroom, c\\u00f4ng ty \\u0111\\u00e3 \\u0111\\u1eb7t thi\\u1ebft k\\u1ebf website b\\u00e1n xe tr\\u1edf th\\u00e0nh k\\u00eanh truy\\u1ec1n th\\u00f4ng ch\\u00ednh trong chi\\u1ebfn l\\u01b0\\u1ee3c kinh doanh th\\u00e0nh c\\u00f4ng c\\u1ee7a m\\u00ecnh. B\\u1edfi l\\u1ebd, website \\u0111\\u00f3ng vai tr\\u00f2 nh\\u01b0 b\\u1ed9 m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n cho th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng hi\\u1ec7u c\\u1ee7a b\\u1ea1n tr\\u00ean n\\u1ec1n t\\u1ea3ng internet. Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ti\\u00eau d\\u00f9ng d\\u1ec5 d\\u00e0ng t\\u00ecm ki\\u1ebfm s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m m\\u1ecdi l\\u00fac, m\\u1ecdi n\\u01a1i th\\u00f4ng qua website. M\\u1ed9t website chuy\\u00ean nghi\\u1ec7p, uy t\\u00edn s\\u1ebd t\\u1ea1o ti\\u1ec1n \\u0111\\u1ec1 l\\u1edbn thuy\\u1ebft ph\\u1ee5